quot%3BCongress%20ko%20Muslim%20vote%20chahiye%2C%20candidate%20kyun%20nahi%20(Congress%20wants%20Muslim%20votes%2C%20but%20why%20not%20candidates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20all%20this%20reasons%2C%20I%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20face%20and%20I%20have%20no%20answers%20to%20Muslims%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khan%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20also%20said%20he%20is%20also%20resigning%20from%20the%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20Campaign%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F72srjkn8_congress-leader-letter_625x300_27_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20image%20caption%20here%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20contesting%2017%20out%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar).%20They%20are%20constituents%20of%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuhammed%20Arif%20Khan%20was%20in%20race%20for%20a%20ticket%20from%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%2C%20but%20the%20party%20chose%20city%20unit%20president%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20for%20the%20constituency.%20He%20had%20contested%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%20from%20Chandivali%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20he%20lost%20by%20409%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20separately%20to%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20said%20the%20Congress%20it%20seems%20has%20deviated%20from%20its%20long-held%20ideology%20of%20inclusivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20said%20he%20was%20inundated%20with%20calls%20from%20organisations%20representing%20minorities%20and%20party%20workers%20from%20these%20social%20groups%2C%20asking%20why%20the%20Congress%20has%20ignored%20them%20while%20allotting%20tickets%20for%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%