l%20strike%20rate%20is%20160%20and%20you%20need%20that%2C%20you%20need%20that%20firepower.%20If%20Virat%20opens%20up%20the%20batting%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20it%20will%20allow%20the%20combination%20of%2011%20to%20be%20in%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20which%20you%20want.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20you%20might%20see%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shivam%20Dube%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107521-shivam-dubey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fa%3E%20playing%2C%20if%20he's%20there%20in%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20see%20guys%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rinku%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106742-rinku-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERinku%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20playing%2011%20as%20well.%20But%20if%20Virat%20bats%20at%20number%20three%2C%20that%20might%20not%20happen.%20So%20that's%20a%20big%20challenge.%20The%20other%20thing%2C%20if%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20is%20playing%2C%20what%20can%20happen%20as%20he's%20actually%20been%20bowling%20regularly%20in%20the%20nets.%20So%20what%20you%20can%20do%20is%20you%20can%20actually%20play%20proper%20five%20bowlers%20and%20maybe%20have%20him%20as%20a%20sixth%20bowler%2C%20as%20an%20option%20to%20keep%20it.%20Otherwise%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20batting%20order%2C%20no%20one%20bowls.%20No%20one%20bowls%20in%20top%20six%20and%20that's%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20what%20we%20have%20as%20Indian%20cricket.%20And%20that's%20what%20we%20need%20to%20consider%20that%20as%20well.%20So%20for%20me%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20then%20Virat%20bats%20at%20number%20three.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tom%20Moody%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41266-thomas-masson-moody-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETom%20Moody%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%20that%20since%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20being%20played%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20is%