%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20Vadra%20had%20expressed%20similar%20intentions%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Amethi%20expect%20him%20to%20represent%20their%20constituency%20if%20he%20thinks%20of%20becoming%20a%20member%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20returns%2C%20they%20will%20ensure%20the%20person's%20victory%20with%20a%20huge%20margin%2C%20they%20also%20expect%20that%20if%20I%20take%20my%20first%20step%20in%20politics%2C%20and%20think%20of%20becoming%20an%20MP%2C%20then%20I%20should%20represent%20Amethi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20on%20April%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20posters%20featuring%20Robert%20Vadra%2C%20appeared%20outside%20the%20party's%20office%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20the%20Gauriganj%20area%20of%20Amethi.%20This%20raised%20speculations%20of%20a%20possible%20ticket%20for%20Vadra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20Vadra%2C%20however%2C%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20constituencies%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20Congress%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%C2%A0%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20likely%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Amethi%20seats%2C%20respectively.%20A%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20April%2026%20and%20nominations%20can%20be%20filed%20next%20week%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmriti%20Irani%20defeated%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Amethi.%20Irani%20has%20been%20fielded%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20from%20the%20seat%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20seat%20agreement%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20contest%2017%20seats%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20the%2