lection%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Irfan%20Pathan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F607-irfan-pathan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIrfan%20Pathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20recalled%20the%20time%20when%20he%20was%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20team%20following%20an%20injury.%20Irfan%2C%20who%20made%20his%20India%20debut%20in%202003%2C%20played%2029%20Tests%2C%20120%20ODIs%20and%2024%20T20Is%20for%20the%20country%20between%202003%20and%202012.%20His%20career%2C%20however%2C%20was%20hampered%20by%20recurring%20knee%20injuries.%20While%20he%20played%20his%20last%20game%20for%20India%20in%202012%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20feature%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20until%202019%2C%20hoping%20to%20earn%20a%20recall%20some%20day.%20However%2C%20in%20January%202020%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20announce%20his%20retirement%20from%20all%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20responding%20to%20a%20query%20on%20%26quot%3Brecency%20bias%26quot%3B%2C%20Irfan%20criticised%20former%20India%20opener%20Krishnamachari%20Srikkanth%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20back%20then%2C%20for%20kicking%20him%20out%20of%20the%20team%20after%20an%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20when%20Srikanth%20sir%20was%20the%20selector.%20I%20got%20injured%20and%20got%20kicked%20out%20and%20never%20played%20for%20India.%20No%20that's%20the%20truth.%20And%20i%20have%20no%20qualms%20about%20it.%20I%20have%20huge%20respect%20for%20you.%20That%20time%2C%20the%20mindset%20was%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Irfan%20Pathan%2C%20Commentator%20%26amp%3B%20Cricket%20Expert%20with%20IPL%20official%20TV%20Broadcaster%2C%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports%20Press%20Room%20Show%2C%20Ticket%20to%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20explained%20how%20selectors%20back%20then%20often%20neglected%20a%20player's%20match-winning%20performances%20in%20the%20past%20after%20just%20one%20bad%20tour%20or%20an%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20selectors%20shouldn't%20judge%20a%20player%20after%20just%20one%20good%20season%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20come%20to%202020s%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Wriddhiman%20Saha%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1088-wriddhiman-saha-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWriddhiman%20Saha%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20literally%20out%20of%20the%20team%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20due%20to%20injury.%20What%20happened%20when%20he%20got%20fit%3F%20He%20got%20picked%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20XI.%20And%20one%20year%20is%20a%20long%20time.%20But%20because%20Indian%20team%20thought%20was%20Indian%20team%20has%20done%20for%20him%20in%20the%20past%20before%20getting%20injured%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20undervalue%20that.%20We%20want%20to%20value%20that.%20So%20when%20someone%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20you%20should%20not%20forget%20what%20the%20guy%20has%20done%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20before%20the%20IPL.%20And%20its%20not%20too%20far%20away%20I%20am%20talking%20about.%20Just%20because%20some%20guys%20are%20playing%20well%20in%20IPL%2C%20you%20think%20we%20should%20pick%20them.%20But%20don't%20forget%20the%20guys%20(who%20have%20done%20well%20in%20the%20past)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714189500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3gb61nco_irfan-pathan-team-india-afp_625x300_26_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fex-india-stars-i-was-kicked-out-revelation-amid-t20-world-cup-selection-debate-5529770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20India%20all-rounder%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20selectors%20shouldn't%20judge%20a%20player%20after%20just%20one%20good%20season%20in%20the%20IPL.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20India%20Stares%20At%20Severe%20Water%20Crisis%20As%20Reservoirs%20Plunge%20To%20Mere%2017%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20region%2C%20encompassing%20states%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20has%20significantly%20reduced%20water%20storage%20compared%20to%20historical%20averages%20at%20just%2017%20per%20cent%20of%20reservoir%20capacity%2C%20according%20to%20the%20recent%20bulletin%20of%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20(CWC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bulletin%20released%20by%20the%20CWC%20concerning%20reservoir%20storage%20levels%20across%20various%20regions%20of%20India%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%2042%20reservoirs%20under%20CWC%20monitoring%20in%20the%20southern%20region%20have%20a%20total%20live%20storage%20capacity%20of%2053.334%20BCM%20(billion%20cubic%20meters).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20latest%20report%2C%20the%20total%20live%20storage%20available%20in%20these%20reservoirs%20stands%20at%208.865%20BCM%2C%20representing%20only%2017%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20total%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20figure%20is%20considerably%20lower%20compared%20to%20the%20storage%20levels%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%20(29%20per%20cent)%20and%20the%20ten-year%20average%20for%20the%20corresponding%20period%20(23%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reduced%20storage%20levels%20in%20the%20southern%20region%20are%20indicative%20of%20worsening%20water%20scarcity%20and%20potential%20challenges%20for%20irrigation%2C%20drinking%20water%20supply%20and%20hydroelectric%20power%20generation%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20eastern%20region%2C%20comprising%20states%20like%20Assam%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20has%20shown%20a%20positive%20improvement%20in%20water%20storage%20levels%20compared%20to%20last%20year%20and%20the%20ten-year%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulletin%20highlighted%20that%20in%20this%20region%2C%2023%20monitored%20reservoirs%20with%20a%20total%20live%20storage%20capacity%20of%2020.430%20BCM%20currently%20hold%207.889%20BCM%20of%20water%2C%20representing%2039%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20total%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20an%20improvement%20over%20the%20storage%20levels%20from%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%20(34%20per%20cent)%20and%20the%20ten-year%20average%20(34%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20less%20optimistic%20in%20other%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20region%2C%20consisting%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20reports%20storage%20levels%20of%2011.771%20BCM%2C%20which%20is%2031.7%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20capacity%20of%2049%20monitored%20reservoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20notably%20lower%20compared%20to%20the%20storage%20levels%20of%20the%20previous%20year%20(38%20per%20cent)%20and%20the%20ten-year%20average%20(32.1%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20northern%20and%20central%20regions%20also%20show%20declines%20in%20water%20storage%20levels%20compared%20to%20historical%20averages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20analysis%20provided%20in%20the%20bulletin%20categorizes%20reservoir%20storage%20across%20various%20river%20basins%20as%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20than%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bclose%20to%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bdeficient%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20deficient%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20river%20basins%20like%20Brahmaputra%2C%20Narmada%20and%20Tapi%20are%20marked%20as%20having%20better-than-normal%20storage%20levels%2C%20whereas%20basins%20like%20Cauvery%20and%20east%20flowing%20rivers%20between%20Mahanadi%20and%20Pennar%20are%20classified%20as%20highly%20deficient.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%