new%20legislation%20signed%20by%20Gov.%20Bill%20Lee.%20The%20bill%20marks%20a%20significant%20expansion%20of%20gun%20access%20since%20the%20Nashville%20school%20shooting%2C%20despite%20opposition%20from%20some%20families%20and%20districts%20preferring%20active-duty%20officers%20for%20safety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftennessee-governor-signs-bills-to-allow-armed-teachers-nearly-a-year-after-deadly-nashville-shooting%2Farticleshow%2F109638698.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftennessee-governor-signs-bills-to-allow-armed-teachers-nearly-a-year-after-deadly-nashville-shooting%2Famp_articleshow%2F109638698.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftennessee-governor-signs-bills-to-allow-armed-teachers-nearly-a-year-after-deadly-nashville-shooting%2Famp_articleshow%2F109638698.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trillions%20Of%20%26quot%3BLoud%2C%20Sexually%20Aroused%26quot%3B%20Cicadas%20Set%20To%20Engulf%20US%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThey're%20loud.%20They're%20sexually%20aroused.%20And%20for%20one%20special%2C%20cacophonous%20month%20up%20to%20a%20trillion%20of%20them%20will%20engulf%20suburbs%20and%20woodlands%20across%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20cicada%20%26quot%3Bbroods%26quot%3B%20are%20set%20for%20a%20rare%20double%20emergence%20that%20last%20occurred%20in%201803%2C%20when%20Thomas%20Jefferson%20was%20president%20and%20the%20United%20States%20purchased%20Louisiana%20from%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20another%20natural%20wonder%20just%20weeks%20after%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20across%20much%20of%20the%20country%20has%20gripped%20scientists%20and%20the%20public%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Insects%20of%20history'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECicadas%20comprise%20a%20diverse%20family%20of%20over%203%2C000%20insect%20species%20found%20globally%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20lives%20spent%20underground%20in%20a%20larval%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20emerge%20as%20adults%20to%20transform%20and%20mate%2C%20with%20some%20species%20appearing%20annually%20and%20others%2C%20known%20as%20periodical%20cicadas%2C%20synchronizing%20their%20emergence%20every%2013%20or%2017%20years.%20Mathematicians%20have%20long%20been%20intrigued%20by%20the%20question%20of%20why%20periodical%20cicadas%20follow%20prime%20number%20cycles%2C%20despite%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20clear%20evolutionary%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20event%20involves%20the%2013-year%20Brood%20XIX%2C%20currently%20emerging%20in%20the%20Carolinas%2C%20followed%20by%20the%2017-year%20Brood%20XIII%20in%20the%20Midwest.%20There%20could%20be%20a%20small%20area%20of%20overlap%20in%20central%20Illinois.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20do%20come%20out%2C%20they%20come%20out%20in%20big%20numbers%2C%20parents%20get%20excited%2C%20the%20kids%20get%20excited%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20entomologist%20Gene%20Kritsky%20of%20Mount%20St.%20Joseph%20University%2C%20who%20developed%20the%20Cicada%20Safari%20app%20for%20citizen-scientists%20to%20gather%20data%2C%20explaining%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20harmless%20red-eyed%20bugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20%26quot%3Bcreatures%20of%20history%26quot%3B%3A%20People%20vividly%20recall%20where%20they%20were%20when%20the%20cicadas%20last%20appeared%20in%20their%20area%2C%20and%20these%20personal%20stories%20become%20embedded%20in%20family%20lore%2C%20passed%20down%20to%20the%20next%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20witnessing%20a%20rare%20eclipse%2C%20Kritsky%20notes%20that%20there's%20a%20unique%20value%20in%20seeing%20scientific%20predictions%20come%20to%20life.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20science%20does%3A%20you%20come%20up%20with%20hypotheses%20that%20lead%20to%20predictions%2C%20the%20predictions%20are%20verified...and%20there's%20something%20valuable%20about%20this%20in%20a%20time%20when%20some%20people%20have%20thought%20to%20disregard%20science.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientific%20marvel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelatively%20defenseless%2C%20periodical%20cicadas'%20strength%20lies%20in%20their%20sheer%20numbers%20that%20satiates%20the%20appetites%20of%20the%20birds%2C%20foxes%2C%20racoons%2C%20turtles%20and%20other%20predators%2C%20John%20Lill%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20biology%20at%20the%20George%20Washington%20University%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20paper%20published%20in%20Science%2C%20Lill%20and%20colleagues%20revealed%20a%20number%20of%20broader%20impacts%20on%20the%20wider%20ecosystem.%20They%20found%20the%202021%20emergence%20of%20Brood%20X%20in%20the%20capital%20Washington%20proved%20a%20windfall%20for%20insectivorous%20birds%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20caterpillar%20populations%20as%20the%20birds%20focused%20on%20feasting%20on%20the%20cicadas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reprieve%20allowed%20caterpillars%20to%20thrive%2C%20resulting%20in%20increased%20consumption%20of%20oak%20saplings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20new%20research%20showed%20that%20%26quot%3Bmast%20years%26quot%3B%20--%20when%20oak%20trees%20produce%20an%20abundance%20of%20acorns%20--%20follow%20like%20clockwork%20two%20years%20after%20cicada%20emergence.%20More%20acorns%20support%20larger%20populations%20of%20the%20mammals%20that%20feed%20on%20them%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20more%20Lyme%20disease%20risk%20for%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20cicadas%20determine%20when%20the%20masting%20event%20occurs%2C%20which%20then%20determine%20when%20the%20Lyme%20disease%20occurs%2C%20just%20sort%20of%20highlights%20that%20there%20are%20these%20potentially%20longer%20term%20ecological%20impacts%20that%20reverberate%20for%20years%20after%20the%20cicada%20emergence%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20of%20course%20there's%20the%20males'%20distinctive%20--%20and%20deafening%20--%20mating%20chorus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20several%20calls%20about%20a%20noise%20in%20the%20air%20that%20sounds%20like%20a%20siren%2C%20or%20a%20whine%2C%20or%20a%20roar%2C%26quot%3B%20Newberry%20Sheriff's%20Office%20in%20South%20Carolina%20posted%20this%20week%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20impacts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChris%20Simon%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Connecticut%2C%20who%20studies%20the%20chemical%20changes%20in%20cicada%20DNA%20that%20track%20their%20life%20cycle%2C%20warns%20that%20climate%20change%20is%20disrupting%20their%20internal%20clocks.%20As%20the%20US%20warms%20up%2C%20a%20longer%20plant%20growing%20season%20provides%20more%20food%2C%20accelerating%20cicada%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20predict%20that%20more%2017%20year%20cicadas%20will%20turn%20into%20permanent%2013%20year%20cicadas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20eventually%20that%20trait%20will%20be%20genetically%20assimilated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20that%20means%20for%20the%20species%20in%20the%20long%20run%20is%20hard%20to%20know.%20It's%20also%20unclear%20whether%20drastic%20land%20transformation%20since%20the%20colonial%20period%20has%20been%20a%20net%20positive%20or%20negative%20for%20cicadas%2C%20said%20Lill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20many%20historic%20broods%20have%20been%20lost%20to%20rampant%20deforestation.%20But%20the%20remaining%20broods%20are%20flourishing%20in%20suburban%20environments%20where%20well-lit%20trees%20provide%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20females%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20adults%20die%2C%20the%20newly%20hatched%20cicada%20nymphs%20fall%20off%20the%20trees%20and%20burrow%20underground%2C%20and%20the%20cycle%20begins%20anew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20