oogle%20as%20well%20as%20Amazon's%20cloud%20service%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20even%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20long-shot%20demand%20-%20university%20administrators%20and%20lawmakers%20have%20for%20decades%20rejected%20the%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%2C%20Sanctions%20movement%20against%20Israel%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20antisemitic%20because%20it%20calls%20into%20question%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20Jewish%20state%20and%20singles%20out%20the%20policies%20of%20one%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20fiercely%20opposed%20by%20many%20donors%20and%20alumni%2C%20and%20what's%20more%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20BDS%20concept%20is%20discouraged%20by%20laws%20in%20more%20than%20half%20of%20US%20states%2C%20including%20New%20York%20and%20California.%20That's%20unlikely%20to%20change%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20consistently%20opposed%20all%20forms%20of%20antisemitism%2C%20including%20discrimination%20against%20and%20demonization%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20through%20the%20BDS%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20California%20Assembly%20Democratic%20Caucus%20Chair%20Rick%20Chavez%20Zbur.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20strongly%20oppose%20any%20attempts%20to%20change%20laws%20protecting%20against%20such%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20it's%20gaining%20proponents%2C%20especially%20among%20students%20at%20elite%20universities%20since%20Oct.%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20attacked%20Israel%20and%20sparked%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20that%20has%20killed%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey're%20chanting%20on%20college%20grounds%2C%20waving%20Palestinian%20flags%2C%20wearing%20keffiyehs%20and%20beating%20drums.%20Encampments%20have%20sprouted%20on%20campuses%2C%20including%20at%20Harvard%20where%20about%2030%20tents%20currently%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20John%20Harvard%20statue%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Harvard%20Crimson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20protesters%2C%20including%20at%20Columbia%20and%20Berkeley%2C%20have%20threatened%20Jewish%20students%20and%20expressed%20support%20for%20Hamas%2C%20which%20is%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20has%20left%20universities%20struggling%20to%20balance%20the%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20with%20the%20need%20for%20maintaining%20order%20and%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20students.%20But%20on%20the%20question%20of%20divestment%2C%20they%20are%20unmoved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarvard%2C%20which%20has%20the%20largest%20US%20endowment%20at%20almost%20%2451%20billion%2C%20made%20clear%20this%20month%20it%20%26quot%3Bopposes%20calls%20for%20a%20policy%20of%20boycotting%20Israel%20and%20its%20academic%20institutions.%26quot%3B%20Brown%20refused%20to%20acknowledge%20BDS%20demands%20while%20students%20led%20an%20eight-day%20hunger%20strike.%20Yale%20this%20week%20wouldn't%20even%20consider%20a%20proposal%20to%20divest%20from%20weapons%20makers%20and%20instead%20police%20rounded%20up%20protesters%20outside%20of%20the%20Schwarzman%20Center%2C%20arresting%20more%20than%2040%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBDS%20supporters%20take%20inspiration%20from%20the%20drive%20to%20isolate%20South%20Africa%20during%20the%20apartheid%20era%20-%20including%20actions%20taken%20at%20the%20time%20by%20Columbia%2C%20Michigan%20State%20and%20California%20universities%20-%20and%20recent%20pushes%20for%20colleges%20to%20address%20fossil%20fuel%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20at%20Michigan%20State%2C%20where%20groups%20of%20students%20are%20camped%20in%20tents%20in%20People's%20Park%2C%20there's%20no%20appetite%20for%20severing%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDivestment%20would%20conflict%20with%20stewarding%20the%20institution's%20financial%20health%2C%20would%20increase%20investment%20risks%2C%20and%20limit%20returns%20and%20jeopardize%20the%20assurance%20resources%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20available%20now%20and%20for%20future%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sandy%20Pierce%2C%20chair%20of%20Michigan%20State%20University's%20board%2C%20speaking%20earlier%20this%20month%20at%20a%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColumbia%20in%20February%20declined%20a%20proposal%20to%20withdraw%20financial%20support%20from%20Israel%2C%20months%20before%20students%20set%20up%20tents%20on%20the%20Morningside%20Heights%20campus%20and%20created%20a%20standoff%20with%20the%20university%20that%20resulted%20in%20more%20than%20100%20arrests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERay%20Guerrero%2C%2027%2C%20who's%20studying%20for%20a%20masters%20in%20public%20health%2C%20helped%20pen%20the%20divestment%20proposal%20for%20the%20Columbia%20University%20Apartheid%20Divest%20coalition.%20The%20group%20has%20a%20litany%20of%20demands%2C%20including%20cutting%20ties%20to%20Israeli%20academic%20institutions%2C%20defunding%20public%20safety%20and%20reparations%20for%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20New%20York.%20Guerrero%20understands%20the%20goals%20are%20lofty%20for%20the%20immediate%20term%2C%20but%20stresses%20the%20main%20focus%20for%20now%20is%20disclosure%20and%20divestment%20around%20Columbia's%20%2413.6%20billion%20endowment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELayla%20Saliba%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20studying%20for%20a%20masters%20in%20social%20work%2C%20is%20part%20of%20CUAD's%20research%20team%2C%20which%20she%20said%20has%20been%20studying%20the%20school's%20financial%20disclosures%2C%20including%20its%20tax%20forms%20and%2013Fs%20disclosures%20to%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20only%20able%20to%20get%20about%200.6%25%20of%20their%20investments%20as%20public%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%2013F%20discloses%20just%20%2447%20million%20of%20its%20holdings%2C%20with%20the%20vast%20majority%20stock%20in%20Warren%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathaway.%20That%20leaves%20billions%20of%20dollars%20undisclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20really%20concerning%20because%20our%20endowment%2C%20yes%2C%20it's%20funded%20by%20benefactors%2C%20it's%20funded%20by%20donors%2C%20but%20a%20portion%20of%20that%20is%20also%20funded%20with%20our%20tuition%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Saliba%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20feel%20that%20as%20students%2C%20we%20need%20to%20have%20more%20transparency%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversities%20say%20the%20protesters'%20claims%20aren't%20accurate.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20California%2C%20which%20opposes%20any%20boycott%20of%20Israel%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20tuition%20fees%20are%20not%20used%20for%20investments.%20College%20endowments%20are%20almost%20always%20funded%20with%20donations%20and%20investment%20gains.%20What's%20more%2C%20they%20fund%20financial%20aid%20for%20students%20and%20other%20operating%20expenses%20such%20as%20teacher%20salaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20challenge%20isn't%20just%20ideological.%20Endowments%20typically%20don't%20hold%20large%20concentrations%20of%20single%20stocks%20as%20they%20used%20to%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20activists%20targeted%20companies%20operating%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEndowments%20have%20long%20relied%20on%20external%20managers%2C%20including%20private%20equity%20firms%20and%20hedge%20funds.%20Almost%20700%20institutions%20hold%20about%20%24840%20billion%20in%20endowment%20assets.%20They%20also%20use%20ETFs%2C%20index%20funds%20or%20mutual%20funds%20that%20pool%20hundreds%20of%20stocks%20and%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20private%20equity%2C%20a%20school's%20money%20may%20be%20locked%20up%20for%20several%20years%2C%20without%20an%20option%20to%20withdraw%2C%20while%20hedge%20fund%20managers%20can%20rapidly%20move%20in%20and%20out%20of%20securities%20without%20disclosing%20their%20trades%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20active%20strategies%20are%20not%20buying%20stocks%20to%20hold%20on%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Philip%20Zecher%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Michigan%20State%20University's%20%244%20billion%20fund.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20looking%20to%20make%20money%20off%20trading.%20It's%20not%20like%20your%20grandmother%20buying%20AT%26amp%3BT%20stock%20and%20sitting%20on%20it%20for%2050%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20against%20fossil%20fuel%20investment%2C%20a%20cause%20championed%20by%20students%20for%20decades%2C%20also%20shows%20how%20hard%20it%20can%20be%20to%20implement%20divestment.%20Universities%20largely%20haven't%20switched%20strategies%20to%20sell%20holdings%2C%20which%20are%20frequently%20tied%20up%20in%20long-term%20private%20equity%20funds%2C%20even%20as%20they've%20committed%20to%20policies%20designed%20to%20reduce%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20on%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setbacks%20and%20opposition%2C%20some%20pro-Palestine%20protesters%20are%20undeterred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20a%20no%20for%20now%2C%20but%20students%20will%20keep%20pushing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lumisa%20Bista%2C%20a%20junior%20studying%20astrophysics%20at%20Yale%2C%20who%20was%20among%20protesters%20at%20the%20university%20who%20slept%20overnight%20at%20Beinecke%20Plaza%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20keep%20pushing.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714184460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fos9b3jeg_columbia-university-afp-_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwell-risk-expulsion-arrest-pro-palestine-protests-continue-in-us-5533273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20cause%20celebre%20is%20ringing%20out%20across%20Harvard%20Yard%2C%20Columbia's%20South%20Lawn%2C%20Yale's%20Beinecke%20Plaza%20and%20UC%2