ecipe-for-gajar-ka-halwa-history-winter-dessert%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elip-smacking%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20has%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20Onam%20%3Cem%3Esaadya%3C%2Fem%3E%20platter.%20The%20best%20part%20of%20this%20dish%20is%20that%20you%20can%20prepare%20it%20with%20a%20seasonal%20fruit%20or%20any%20vegetable%20of%20your%20choice.%20This%20summer%2C%20why%20not%20try%20it%20with%20mango%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Besara%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FSZNXB8a-FEU%3Fsi%3DYWRcP3-UnYPdsRTZ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20traditional%20flavourful%20gravy%20made%20with%20ground%20mustard%20seeds%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebesara%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20famous%20not%20just%20for%20its%20delectable%20taste%20but%20also%20for%20its%20religious%20significance.%20The%20dish%20is%20one%20of%20the%2056%20that%20are%20offered%20as%20%3Cem%3Emahaprasad%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20Puri%20Shree%20Jagannath%20Temple.%20There%20are%20numerous%20variations%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebesara%3C%2Fem%3E%20depending%20on%20the%20hero%20ingredient.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Cem%3Emaccha%20besara%3C%2Fem%3E%20refers%20to%20fish%20in%20mustard%20gravy%20while%20the%20%3Cem%3Epoi%20chingudi%20besara%3C%2Fem%3E%20features%20shrimp%20and%20spinach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Lal%20Maas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fx6VBBUDXQbo%3Fsi%3DgPOPnmiShzFM7zTC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20delicacy%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20%3Cem%3Elal%20maas%3C%2Fem%3E%20literally%20tran