h%20Bollapally%20lived%20in%20poverty%20as%20a%20child.%20He%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20different%20route%20and%20started%20growing%20flowers.%20Today%2C%20with%20a%20farmland%20of%20over%2050%20acres%2C%20he%20is%20earning%20crores%20every%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348172%2Fflower-farmer-in-karnataka-bengaluru-srikanth-bollapally-grows-roses-gerbera-carnations-making-crores-annually%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%2077-YO%20Worked%20For%20a%20Decade%20After%20Retirement%20to%20Bring%20a%20River%20Back%20to%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20balmy%20February%20noon%2C%2077-year-old%20Vaijinath%20Jagannath%20Ghongade%20stood%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Manganga%20river%20in%20Solapur%20district%2C%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20ashamed%20benefitting%20from%20the%20pension%20I%20got%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20but%20doing%20nothing%20in%20return.%20Having%20reflected%20for%20several%20days%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20tour%20the%20stretch%20of%20the%20river%20on%20foot%20and%20study%20its%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20this%20river%2C%20which%20flows%20close%20to%20my%20village%20Wadegaon%20in%20Sangola%20taluka%2C%20and%20supports%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20hundreds%2C%20was%20slowly%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20undertaking%20of%20cleaning%20the%2075-km%20stretch%20of%20Manganga%20river%20flowing%20from%20Sangli%20to%20Solapur%20with%20public%20participation%20was%20started%20in%202016.%20And%20the%20man%20who%20championed%20the%20cause%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337896%2Ftamil-nadu-techie-srikanth-braves-threats-to-grow-forest-palar-river%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target