The%20duo%20aim%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20water%20swimming%20in%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20over%2015%20hours%20in%20the%20boat%2C%20they%20started%20their%20swim%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20motivated%20by%20their%20crew%20and%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Navy.%20The%2032%20km%20swim%20was%20conducted%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20experts%2C%20who%20helped%20the%20swimmers%20navigate%20and%20provided%20nutrition%20during%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20to%20success%20and%20the%20road%20to%20failure%20are%20almost%20exactly%20the%20same.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20practice%2C%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%2C%20along%20with%20belief%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20ability%20that%20differentiates%20between%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20was%20very%20choppy%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20swim%2C%20unlike%20the%20condition%20they%20had%20practised%20in.%20Yet%2C%20the%20two%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20anything%20deter%20them%20that%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20moments%20when%20you%20can%20lose%20your%20breath%20and%20composure.%20The%20water%20can%20be%20very%20unforgiving.%20You%20face%20certain%20life%20and%20death%20moments%2C%20but%20remember%2C%20that%20you%20must%20respect%20the%20process.%20Take%20the%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20hours%20were%20excruciating%2C%20their%20skin%20was%20completely%20burnt%2C%20the%20water%20rough%2C%20and%20their%20energy%20low.%20They%20kept%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20outcome%2C%20and%20their%20goal%20for%20doing%20this%20swim.%20The%20crew%20also%20kept%20cheering%20and%20motivating%20them%2C%20helping%20them%20navigate%20the%20turbulent%20waters.%20It%20was%20a%20test%20of%20their%20mental%20and%20emotional%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20this%20achievement%20has%20a%20very%20high%20spiritual%20and%20cultural%20significance.%20As%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333570%2Fsachin-nag-won-only-gold-medal-swimming-for-india-at-asian-games-sports-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20swimmer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20participated%20in%20several%20challenges%2C%20but%20crossing%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20is%20one%20for%20the%20country.%20While%20we%20were%20swimming%20the%20stretch%2C%20we%20were%20filled%20with%20mixed%20emotions%2C%20of%20celebrating%20the%20spirit%20of%20universal%20brotherhood%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20calling%20out%20to%20the%20nation%20to%20nurture%20swimming%20as%20a%20key%20sport%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20greeted%20by%20hundreds%20of%20young%20boys%20and%20girls%20at%20Dhanushkodi%2C%20making%20it%20all%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20boils%20down%20to%20proper%20planning%20and%20collaboration.%20If%20you%20dream%20and%20put%20in%20the%20effort%2C%20there%20are%20people%20to%20support%20you.%20Dream%20big%2C%20follow%20your%20passion%2C%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20hesitate%20to%20extend%20your%20voice%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%20We%20need%20more%20youngsters%20getting%20into%20swimming%20as%20a%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713873383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bharat%20Sachdeva%20and%20Shaaswat%20Sharma%20swam%20non-stop%20across%20the%20challenging%2032%20km%20stretch%20near%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20in%2010%20hours%2030%20minutes.%20Their%20aim%3F%20To%20promote%