E%3Cstrong%3EGo%20For%20Homemade%2FNatural%20Food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20the%20healthiest%20foods%20are%20the%20ones%20without%20any%20labels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20unlimited%20access%20to%20resources%2C%20the%20best%20thing%20we%20can%20do%20for%20our%20health%20is%20to%20stay%20updated%20and%20informed%20about%20what%20we%20consume.%20There%20are%20multiple%20ways%20for%20us%20to%20inculcate%20safe%20practices%20and%20avail%20homemade%20options%20as%20well.%20Having%20the%20knowledge%20of%20which%20ingredients%20work%20best%20for%20us%20and%20which%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20can%20definitely%20help%20us%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2016-09%2Fdocuments%2Fethylene-oxide.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUS%20EPA%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713857252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348030%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20four%20of%20MDH%20and%20Everest%20group's%20spices%20coming%20under%20the%20scanner%20by%20the%20food%20safety%20agencies%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20here's%20all%20that%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20ethylene%20oxide%2C%20the%20component%20stirring%20the%20pot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348030%2Fmdh-everest-sambhar-masala-fssai-guidelines-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20Did%20Bengaluru